reviewText: Four most enjoyable movies.  Saw comments regarding short run time.  If there was anything missing it was not obvious and did not affect the continuity of the movies.  Am very pleased with the item.

why on earth don't they release the full length versions of roy rogers movies NOT the cut versions his movies run between 65 to 75 min. not 56 min.this is a great loss not to restore his movies he made 19 color movies get these movies restored befor they are all gone.

Seen this before. None of these four movies are full length.
All run about 53 minutes.
That being said and if you just want to watch some old Roy Rogers movies these are in good shape. Each movie on a single disk.
But if you are looking for full length movies forget it
